plot: Jo and Chris have to evade the FBI while investigating the cyber terrorists. Ed receives a treatment plan for his cancer that seems to good to be true. A mysterious woman puts Piper and the Evans family in danger.

Jo and Chris must evade the FBI as they investigate an elusive group of cyber terrorists. Ed's presented with a cancer treatment that seems too good to be true, and a mysterious woman's attempt to reach Piper puts the entire Evans family in danger.—Kendra Chanae Chapman
